Instruction on how to use the applictaion : 
http://localhost:9191/addCustomers = to create records of customers with transactions (please refer customer Json)
http://localhost:9191/customers = to retrieve all customers
http://localhost:9191/transactions = to retrieve all transactions
http://localhost:9191/customers/{customerId} = retrieve customers based on customerId
http://localhost:9191/updateCustomer/{customerId}?transactionAmount = update customer points based on the transactionAmount provided.
http://localhost:9191/updateCustomer/{customerId}/points?startDate&endDate = update customer points based on the date range (3 months old transactions points can be added to existing points).
http://localhost:9191/delete/{customerId} = delete Customer based on customerId
